data.description: Welcome to this spacious 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom haven nestled in the growing community of Celina. With meticulous attention to detail, this property seamlessly combines style and function. It boasts an open floor plan, modern kitchen and ample living spaces create a welcoming place for gathering with loved ones. Enjoy cool evenings out on the covered back patio as you look for stars in the night sky. The elegant master suite offers the perfect place to unwind at the end of the day. Enjoy the convenience of nearby schools, parks and a growing list of new restaurants and retail shopping, creating the perfect blend of comfort and community living.
